~ start
if VoidSlower.is_void_alive()
	Do you want some help?
	- Yes => help_accepted
	- No => help_denied
else
	You did it! => END

~ help_accepted
Let me distract that Void. It will slow them down.
do VoidSlower.slowdown_void()
Bye!
do GameState.global.helper.clear()
=> END

~ help_denied
OK, bye!
=> END
